Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不會中斷的明天也過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}回頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:30.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}悲歎著無止境的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}記憶也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}永遠什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:36.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}讓我認識到那不會留下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我一直在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}在心靈的角落中哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}然而請務必
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不要丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}那高架橋下度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:55.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}喊著「我在後悔」卻走掉的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不會中斷的明天已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我今天依然在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:08.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}為自己添加著無法忘記的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}沒有你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:32.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur4}僕だけが見てた君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:45.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}過去も未来も　かなしみもよろこびも全て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:55.96,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}オトナになるってきっと優しくなることだと信じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:01.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}子供の頃の僕のままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:06.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君のこと守りたいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暗闇から目覚めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:13.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}僕を待ち受けてる彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:23.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二人を隠したこの街に誰も知らない雪が降っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:33.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君が僕の胸に刻まれた一番深い傷跡のようで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:48.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(0,4000)}君が笑うこの世界の歌　取り戻すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:32.22,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur6}只有我看到了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:45.53,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}過去 未來 悲傷 快樂 一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:55.96,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一直相信著成為大人後一定能變得溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:01.80,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在我現在還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:06.17,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就決定要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.89,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}即便在黑暗中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:13.64,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在等待著我的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:23.82,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}藏匿著兩人的這個城市下著無人所知的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:33.03,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像你在我心裡刻下了最深刻的傷痕一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:48.38,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}{\fad(0,4000)}你所歡笑著的這個世界的歌 我一定會取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18年前的3月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月如往常一樣站在這個公園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間差一點就到6點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候 我去了隱匿處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該是去拿忘掉的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手套有沒有拿到就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開隱匿處之後 隨即便見到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面向河坐著的勇氣哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後 我幾乎用最短距離返回路過公園的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月已經不在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家看黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離雛月加代會成為連續誘拐殺人事件第一個被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安度過3月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雛月一起度過第二天的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣就能改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要將事件本身消除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐再等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這周星期六我想出門一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家一起去科學中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 要是約會的話我就給你零花錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實就是約會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也帶到咱家裡來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吃個火鍋啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月的話生日會的時候會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五街區的雛月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全陷入了誘導審問狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次開播的LiveMan好帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Falco是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有見識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六 帶雛月離開家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該說是帶她遠離母親的暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不清楚 教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.88,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家滿腦都在思春 真是火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.72,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到最近為止不也是她們中的一員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧彆扭 跟著一起去不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「嘛」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在耍帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師認為我是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夥 我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六大家一起去科學中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月也會一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那天有件騰不開的要事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有重要的事情沒法去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很想去 但我也有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雛月一起的話 兩個人是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴他們說我星期六要和雛月約會所以不能一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要這麼說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要我星期六早點回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個地方想帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去和她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能到職員室來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個小孩子外出的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單單是去玩 我們是去學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習在家裡也能學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六是加代給家裡幫忙的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫忙？幫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你釋放壓力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事沒有必要對你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼不希望雛月出去的理由是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種理由多少都想得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還是小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事的時候誰來負責？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙居然改變態度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶個這麼面癱的孩子出去有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助朋友和好處壞處沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幫助加代什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還當自己是白馬王子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有關家庭暴力的措詞果然起了反效果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是怎麼想的 加代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和這孩子一起去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少給我思春了 小鬼們！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧 雛月太太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著孩子們喊「思春」可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼太太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是別人家的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一半是我家的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子可是在某方面拿出了幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就幫幫他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是為人父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我家和雛月家挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次到我家來聊聊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加代 進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星 星期六…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多管閒事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下班早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧見到你們 還好跟著過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在跟著我們嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當 當然是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天姑且是沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子穿的衣服還挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為母親愛面子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道雛月家的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過根據對話和她母親的情況 基本都能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是原電視局報導部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加代挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞個什麼勁啊 29歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在半路就把人家給拋棄掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2月27日 星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天是個大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾天雛月的母親的暴力似乎有所減少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好喜歡這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎不見人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得像是在偷偷跑進來一樣很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見到人來的時候 會藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她沒說「你傻嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來看看這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看天象儀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時機挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星前陣子看了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在那邊等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既視感嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡雖然是經常來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我和雛月一起來是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道我喜歡這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才選這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要畫漫畫的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.23,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,想要畫漫畫的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會喜歡到這種地方來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18年前 我記得有過相同的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人來的我 在這裡偶然碰到了雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有什麼關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複著同樣的時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本打算改變未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻在不知不覺中走到了原本的時間軌道上？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月 我來幫你拿上衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會根據我的行動而改變的事情也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信吧 未來是能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能鼓起勇氣過來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要事很快就結束了 我就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會礙事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟好紳士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一她沒遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽到了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟君 真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要結婚嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 在那之前還有個叫聘禮的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月被殺害是在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才是真正的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 廣美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我會去接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明早我會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比平常早了點出門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭和63(1988)年3月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18年前雛月失蹤的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月不會失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18年前和這次的情況有著很大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟君 真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雛月之所以會被盯上是因為平時都是獨自呆在公園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大夥明天可別休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從幾天前這個情況就已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到幼稚園去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天有我跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我想早點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛 陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事才怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.45,OTHER_01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1270,94.8)}請用「極」字造句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.45,OTHER_01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1271.6,144.4)}老師把北極熊吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我也會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用盡可能大的聲音說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴裡面的雛月母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴可能在附近聽著的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我在這裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X日要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼輕易？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是夠傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算到這種地方來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天 我毫無疑問改變了歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到6點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我之後完全沒睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在想爭分奪秒見雛月一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夥 行程沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就去悟家大鬧一番
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家一起去買…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 悟 加代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微過來幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼偏偏是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼辦法 因為前陣子值日的時候幹了蠢事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過居然沒人在等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太薄情了點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是5000
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來18年前也正好是5000円啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為過生日太興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把身上的錢全給花了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是和母親一起做了大量的三明治吃掉了來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們暗地裡做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家都說要自己做 我就幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後的幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們拜託八代老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把雛月的生日也告訴了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想稍微讓你嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕是因為悟無論如何都想要兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的禮物沒趕上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你在做什麼嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她急著要走原來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還差一點的 但是睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在意 事後再給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大夥 用5000円的材料來做三明治吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些錢你全用掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人數一起做三明治非常地愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:19:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和18年前不同 光用一天就全吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朋友真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家送了許多禮物給我和雛月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 藤沼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去送雛月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和藤沼還有大家做朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物明天就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撐過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改變了歷史！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到家的時候 大家已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天積累下來的疲勞已經達到了頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繃緊的心情一口氣放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那麼倒下 像爛泥一樣睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到取消…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安 安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到的只有加代一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天 雛月沒有來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和雛月最後定下的約定沒能達成…
